and then the teams had like about three days, so like two half days and two days to hack. And

00:25:59.599 --> 00:26:03.439
between that they had office hours they could go whenever they were ready. So it was like spread

00:26:03.439 --> 00:26:08.479
out. And then the Friday afternoon was our show and tell or the hack presentation.

