have the time. But I haven't experienced them in a professional organization before, so I'm super

00:26:35.599 --> 00:26:45.280
curious. Kind of on this same topic, I saw Rungua, you had a question about challenges for LLM

00:26:45.280 --> 00:26:53.359
projects. Are you available to ask? Yeah, I think, how to say, lots of companies, we talk about the

